
FUNCTIONS : 
    A function is a block of organized and reusable code
    Function Syntax
    1. DataType FunctionName(Parameter list) { }

    Ex : int add(int num1 , int num2){
        <!-- logic -->
        return result;
    }
    2. Return Type FunctionName() { }

    Functions :
    Function Definition
    Function Declaration
    Function Call

    Types of function : 
    4Types

    1. Return Type with Arguments
    1. Return Type with  No Arguments
    1. No Return Type with Arguments (void)
    1. No Return Type with No Arguments
